node.text:
Reminiscing the good old Bangkok days at the new @pratunamsg (@soithaisoinice ‘s new flagship store) in @bugisjunctionxbugisplus with a medley of their affordable and yet authentic Thai street food with mains starting from $6.90 and skewers beginning at $1.20 🤤

We had a FEAST (as you can see from the flatlay) without breaking the bank! 

Super super love their Premium Tom Yum Mama (the broth was so flavourful and thick thanks to the melted cheese) - drank every single drop of it as well as the Tom Yum Seafood Fried Rice (spicy but darn shiok 👍🏻). Highly recommend y’all to get their Fragrant Fried Pork Belly and Skewers as sides! Oh yes, complete it with a beer tower or iced tea tower! That’s life man!

Can’t wait to head back with my friends for a quick, value-for-money yet satisfying Thai meal! Who wants to go with me? 🙋🏻‍♂️
